{"word":"G360 - ἀναλύω - analýō - an-al-oo'-o - Depart","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναλύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">analýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-al-oo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Depart</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விட்டுப்பிரி, (ஓரிடத்தில் இருந்து)வா"},{"paragraph":"1. to unloose, undo again (woven threads)"},{"paragraph":"2. to depart, break up, to depart from life"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G3089 - λύω - lýō - loo'-o/3089\">G3089</a>; to <i>break up</i>, that is, <i>depart</i> (literally or figuratively): - depart, return.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G179/179\">G179</a>, <a href=\"#/G1955/1955\">G1955</a>, <a href=\"#/G1956/1956\">G1956</a>, <a href=\"#/G2646/2646\">G2646</a>, <a href=\"#/G2647/2647\">G2647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3083/3083\">G3083</a>, <a href=\"#/G3084/3084\">G3084</a>, <a href=\"#/G3085/3085\">G3085</a>, <a href=\"#/G3086/3086\">G3086</a>, <a href=\"#/G3089/3089\">G3089</a>, <a href=\"#/G359/359\">G359</a>, <a href=\"#/G360/360\">G360</a>, <a href=\"#/G487/487\">G487</a>, <a href=\"#/G629/629\">G629</a>, <a href=\"#/G630/630\">G630</a>"}]}